channel.title: Oh man I need a lot of help
channel.description: I have been gone for a long time and when I was here 317 were the shit. Now I see all of these 600+ servers. I want to start another server for fun, I've never really had one that I would call successful. Is there anything I should know? I'm not asking to be spoon-fed, I'm searching around looking and all of the new things, but I just need some help. If anyone would like to tell me anything about the new servers that would be useful I would greatly appreciate it. Are they a lot different from the old servers? More files? Etc...
